		<title>ネタがないから「メイドちゃん」と会話した</title>
		<link>https://www.maid-cafe.work/blog/2018/797</link>
					<comments>https://www.maid-cafe.work/blog/2018/797#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[susumuis]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 05 Dec 2018 10:26:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[ネタ]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[メイドアドベントカレンダー]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.maid-cafe.work/?p=797</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[この記事はメイドアドベントカレンダー2018の5日目です。 メイドアドベントカレンダーが早くも止まってしまう！そうは行かないので「メイドちゃん」（bot）に助けてもらいました。 おやすみメイドちゃん！]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>この記事は<a href="https://adventar.org/calendars/3422">メイドアドベントカレンダー2018</a>の5日目です。</p>
<p>メイドアドベントカレンダーが早くも止まってしまう！そうは行かないので「メイドちゃん」（bot）に助けてもらいました。</p>
<p><a href="http://www.maid-cafe.work/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/a8629bdc0a11a9f74606c6df6e9f930f.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-798" src="http://www.maid-cafe.work/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/a8629bdc0a11a9f74606c6df6e9f930f.png" alt="" width="783" height="444" srcset="https://maidnomad.github.io/web/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/a8629bdc0a11a9f74606c6df6e9f930f.png 783w, https://maidnomad.github.io/web/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/a8629bdc0a11a9f74606c6df6e9f930f-300x170.png 300w, https://maidnomad.github.io/web/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/a8629bdc0a11a9f74606c6df6e9f930f-768x435.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 783px) 100vw, 783px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.maid-cafe.work/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/343371416a454be64215e5fc5c135e82.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-799" src="http://www.maid-cafe.work/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/343371416a454be64215e5fc5c135e82.png" alt="" width="761" height="355" srcset="https://maidnomad.github.io/web/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/343371416a454be64215e5fc5c135e82.png 761w, https://maidnomad.github.io/web/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/343371416a454be64215e5fc5c135e82-300x140.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 761px) 100vw, 761px" /></a><a href="http://www.maid-cafe.work/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/0742f005aafc510009152939af49faf7.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-800" src="http://www.maid-cafe.work/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/0742f005aafc510009152939af49faf7.png" alt="" width="786" height="627" srcset="https://maidnomad.github.io/web/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/0742f005aafc510009152939af49faf7.png 786w, https://maidnomad.github.io/web/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/0742f005aafc510009152939af49faf7-300x239.png 300w, https://maidnomad.github.io/web/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/12/0742f005aafc510009152939af49faf7-768x613.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px" /></a></p>
<p>おやすみメイドちゃん！</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
